Revision history for Ganglia-Gmetric-XS

1.04  2012-04-03
  * Fixed semantic bug
    (rt75468 https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Bug/Display.html?id=75468)

1.03  2010-11-29
  * added feature to send metadata (group, desc, title).
    (rt63368 https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Bug/Display.html?id=63368)

1.02  2010-10-26
  * support ganglia 3.1.

1.01  2009-04-21
  * fixed some typo.
    thanks to Carlo Marcelo Arenas Belon.

1.00  2008-06-17
  * first stable release.
  * correct mis-usage of gmetric (Ganglia_gmetric). to destory every time.
    thanks a lot for advice by ganglia team.

0.02  2008-05-26
  * fixed some memory leak bugs.
    see README and apply including patch to ganglia.

0.01  2008-05-16
  * Initial release.

